Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:00.55,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:237258,240553}Don't just eat it like that without permission!{NOTE:何１人で勝手に食べてるんだよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.97,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:240553,242972}Even I held back!{NOTE:俺だって我慢してたのに！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.80,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:242972,244807}First come, first served.{NOTE:早い者勝ちなのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:05.85,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:244807,245850}That's unfair!{NOTE:ずるいぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.43,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:245850,247435}Unfair! Unfair! Unfair!{NOTE:ずるいぞずるいぞずるいぞ～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:10.77,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:247435,250772}Hey, cut it out already.{NOTE:おいお前らいいかげんにしろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.89,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:250772,252899}– But Navirou…!\N– But Lute…!{NOTE:—だってハヒルーが！\\N—だってヒュートが！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:18.23,Default,Gamigami,0,0,0,,{TIME:252899,258237}I thought they might have matured,\Nbut I see they haven't changed at all.{NOTE:立派になったと思ったがこういうところはまったく変わっておらんのう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:22.36,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:260031,262366}Whaf fo yo mean?{NOTE:何かおかひいか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:24.86,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:262366,264869}This doesn't feel bad, though.{NOTE:こういう感じっていいなって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.45,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:264869,266454}You mean this face?{NOTE:こんな顔が!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.37,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:266454,268372}All right, let's try it on Avinia!{NOTE:よーしアユリアも！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:32.00,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:268998,272001}I don't think that's what she meant!{NOTE:あのそういうことじゃないと思うよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:35.46,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:274545,275463}Nya-ow…{NOTE:ニャグゥ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.51,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:278591,280510}By the way, Lute, show them what we brought.{NOTE:それより、リュート、あれを。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.59,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:280510,282595}Oh, yeah.{NOTE:ああそうだった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:45.05,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:284305,285056}Here you go.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:47.09,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:285056,287099}That's… my Kinship Stone!{NOTE:これは…俺の！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:53.43,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:289435,293439}Our friends managed to find it when they infiltrated the Black Castle.{NOTE:みんなでブラックキャッスルに乗り込んだときに取り戻してきたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:57.61,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:293439,297610}And it's not just yours –\Nwe have everyone's Kinship Stones.{NOTE:もちろんダン先輩のだけじゃなくみんなの絆石もね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.98,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:299821,301989}I'm back in top form!{NOTE:絶好調～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.32,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:301989,303324}How do I look?{NOTE:どうだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:06.03,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:303324,306035}You finally look like the Dan I know!{NOTE:やっぱりダン先輩にはそれがないとな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:06.99,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:306035,306994}Yup!{NOTE:うん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:13.08,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:306994,313084}I think you all deserve a good rest and should spend New Year's Eve in Hakum Village.{NOTE:皆しばらくゆっくりとハクム村で新しい年を迎えるといい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:15.29,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:313084,315294}Of course, that includes you, Avinia.{NOTE:もちろんアユリアもな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.29,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:315294,316295}Yes sir.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:17.88,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:316295,317880}I'll gladly accept your invitation.{NOTE:そうさせていただきます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:20.25,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:317880,320258}Sure, fine…{NOTE:でさ～…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:21.80,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:320258,321801}But, Chief Omna…{NOTE:オムナ村長。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.96,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:321801,322969}Hmm?{NOTE:うん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:24.92,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:322969,324929}Can we finally eat?{NOTE:そろそろ食べていい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:29.47,Default,Gamigami,0,0,0,,{TIME:327265,329475}I can't believe you guys…{NOTE:まったくお前たちは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:32.27,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:329475,332270}Let's call everyone and start.{NOTE:じゃあ皆を呼んで始めよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:33.68,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:332270,333688}All right!{NOTE:やった～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:44.57,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:342238,344574}Ah, I'm stuffed!{NOTE:あ～おなかいっぱい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:46.15,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:344574,346158}You really ate all you could.{NOTE:あれだけ食べればね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:47.11,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:346158,347118}Yeah.{NOTE:ええ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:50.62,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:347118,350621}I'm sure I'll fall asleep in five seconds when I get home.{NOTE:俺家に戻ったら５秒で寝られる自信ある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:52.37,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:350621,352373}For Navirou it's three seconds.{NOTE:ナビルーは３秒だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:54.33,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:352373,354331}Then it's two seconds for me.{NOTE:なら俺は２秒だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:56.83,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:354331,356836}Then I need only one.{NOTE:なら１秒だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:58.29,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:356836,358296}I know!{NOTE:そうだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:01.79,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:358296,361799}Why don't we get up early tomorrow to see the sunrise?{NOTE:あした早起きして朝日を見に行かないか？}
