Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:09.09,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:363301,369098}I'd like to see the first sunrise of the new year\Ntogether with everyone!{NOTE:新しい年の一番最初の日の出をみんなで一緒に見たいなって！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:10.55,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:369098,370558}That sounds great!{NOTE:それいいね！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:11.55,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:370558,371559}Count me in!{NOTE:大賛成！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:12.68,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:371559,372685}Me too!{NOTE:私も！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:14.27,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:372685,374270}Navirou will go with you, too!{NOTE:ナビルーも行くぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:15.52,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:374270,375521}All right!{NOTE:よーし！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:18.35,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:375521,378357}I'll bet the best view will be from Mosco Hill.{NOTE:やっぱりモスコの丘で見るのがいいよな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:19.19,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:378357,379191}Yeah!{NOTE:うん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:22.57,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:379191,382570}That spot is perfect for viewing sunrises.{NOTE:あそこならすっごく奇麗な朝日が見られるよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:24.40,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:382570,384405}Okay, then it's decided!{NOTE:じゃ…決定！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:25.99,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:384405,385990}Navirou will high five too!{NOTE:ナビルーもタッチ～！}
