Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:39.10,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:454976,459105}Lute's home is also Navirou's home.{NOTE:リュートの家ということはつまりナビルーの家でもある！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:41.94,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:459105,461941}Yeah, but you should've told me about this.{NOTE:お前なぁ先に言えよ。}
