Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.28,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:474036,475287}That's terrific!{NOTE:よろしくね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:56.33,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:475287,476330}Yeah.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:57.83,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:476330,477832}All right!{NOTE:よ～し！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:59.37,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:477832,479375}Numbers!{NOTE:ナンバーズのみんな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:00.71,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:479375,480710}Avinia!{NOTE:アユリア！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.42,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:480710,483421}Welcome to my and Cheval's house!{NOTE:ようこそ俺とシュヴァルの家へ！}
