Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:17.60,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:494223,497601}Okay! Let's fall asleep already and get up as soon as possible!{NOTE:よーし！早く寝てあしたは一番に起きるぞ！}
