Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:29.86,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:506027,509864}This is the first time in a while, Avinia.{NOTE:アユリア。こうやって寝るのは久しぶりでしょ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:31.53,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:509864,511532}Have a good rest.{NOTE:ゆっくりおやすみなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:32.82,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:511532,512825}Thank you.{NOTE:ありがとう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:35.03,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:512825,515036}Good night, Fifi.{NOTE:おやすみなさいティティ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:46.67,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:524086,526672}A lot has happened this year…{NOTE:本当に色々あったのう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:52.72,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:527882,532720}Lute's group, who couldn't even Ride On at first…{NOTE:最初はまともにライドオンさえできなかったリュートたちが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:54.84,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:532720,534847}…not only became full-fledged Riders…{NOTE:…無事ライダーとなり…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:59.35,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:534847,539351}…but soon left this village to stop the Black Blight.{NOTE:…黒の凶気を止めるためにこの村を旅立っていった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:03.23,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:539351,543230}And even though there were some breakups along the way…{NOTE:途中様々な別れもあったが…}
