Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:10.23,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:548694,550237}It's all over, isn't it?{NOTE:終わったんだね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:14.03,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:550237,554033}The power of our kinship put an end to it.{NOTE:終わらせたんだ…みんなの絆の力が。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:19.87,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:557036,559872}This year is nearly over now.{NOTE:そろそろことしも終わりじゃな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:36.55,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:572885,576555}I hope this next year will be good to everyone.{NOTE:皆がよき年を迎えられますよう…}
