Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:04.76,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:662766,664768}Fifi…{NOTE:ティティ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.85,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:664768,666854}Avinia.{NOTE:アユリア。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:10.60,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:666854,670608}From now on, you can think of me as your big sister.{NOTE:これからは私をお姉さんだと思ってくれていいのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:21.28,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:679491,681285}It's so warm…{NOTE:あったかい…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:25.91,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:682453,685915}This fluffiness is my pride.{NOTE:このモフモフは私の自慢なの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:28.41,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:685915,688417}You're welcome to plunge in anytime.{NOTE:いつでも飛び込んでいらっしゃい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:30.29,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:688417,690294}I'll always be by your side.{NOTE:ずっとそばにいるから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:31.29,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:690294,691295}Always?{NOTE:ずっと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:32.96,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:691295,692963}Yeah.{NOTE:ええ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:36.38,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:692963,696383}Let me serve you as your Navigator from now on.{NOTE:これからはあなたのナビとしてずっとお供させて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.64,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:702306,704642}Thank you, Fifi…{NOTE:ありがとう、ティティ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:57.57,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:710022,717571}One day I was suddenly taken away by people who called themselves the Ebon Riders.{NOTE:私は……ある日突然ﾌﾞﾗｯｸﾗｲﾀﾞｰｽﾞと名乗る人たちに連れ去られ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:12:02.78,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:717571,722785}Then Frostfang and I were locked in the Black Castle.{NOTE:そして…ﾋｮｳｶﾞとﾌﾞﾗｯｸｷｬｯｽﾙに閉じ込められたの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:08.83,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:723786,728832}In that castle, there were four high ranked Riders.{NOTE:ブラックキャッスルには四天王と呼ばれる４人のライダーがいた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:13.71,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:728832,733712}Mad, Wrath, Shadow, and Gale.{NOTE:マッド、ラース、シャドウ、そしてゲイルの４人ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:16.00,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:733712,736006}But there was one more…{NOTE:それともう一人…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.84,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:736006,737841}One more?{NOTE:もう一人？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:19.34,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:737841,739343}His name is Anvis.{NOTE:彼の名はアンヴィス。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:20.67,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:739343,740678}Anvis…?{NOTE:アンヴィス…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.59,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:740678,742596}What was he like?{NOTE:いったいどんな人なの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:25.22,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:742596,745224}I don't really know.{NOTE:私にも分からない…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:29.22,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:745224,749228}He was always wearing a mask, so I didn't see his face.{NOTE:仮面を着けていて素顔は分からないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:31.81,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:749228,751814}I wonder what their goal could be…?{NOTE:彼らの目的っていったい…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:34.69,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:751814,754692}I tried to find out.{NOTE:そのことは私も尋ねてみた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:38.23,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:754692,758237}I asked one of the four Ebon Riders, Gale.{NOTE:四天王の一人ゲイルって人に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:41.99,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:759238,761991}I'll say this perfectly clear.{NOTE:一つ言っておく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:44.66,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:761991,764660}Right now, you're powerless.{NOTE:今のお前は無力だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.91,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:764660,766912}You can't do anything by yourself.{NOTE:一人じゃ何にもできない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:51.54,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:767788,771542}Naturally, you don't have the key, or the power to break the chains.{NOTE:当然この鎖の鍵を壊す力もない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.83,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:772751,774837}Do not forget that.{NOTE:忘れるな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:59.63,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:774837,779633}Well, it'd be a different story if you had Wrath's appetite.{NOTE:まっ、ラースの兄貴みたいに鎖をかみちぎれたら話は別だがな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:04.59,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:782177,784596}What do you hope to gain from all of this?{NOTE:あなたたちの目的は何なんですか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:07.30,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:784596,787308}A Kinship Stone, of course.{NOTE:もちろん絆石狩りさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:09.93,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:787308,789935}And from the world's best Rider, too.{NOTE:世界一のライダーのな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:14.73,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:790894,794732}I wonder what they're trying to accomplish by collecting Kinship Stones…{NOTE:絆石を集めてどうするつもりなのかしら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:18.52,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:794732,798527}Anvis wanted to know about some arcane art.{NOTE:アンヴィスは秘術について知りたがってた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:22.69,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:798527,802698}Do you have any memories of it?{NOTE:その秘術のこと……覚えがないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:32.49,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:809246,812499}I don't have… any memories of the past.{NOTE:私には昔の記憶がないから…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.45,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:812499,813459}Huh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:37.00,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:814668,817004}Both about my village…{NOTE:村の記憶も…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.96,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:817004,818964}…and about my family.{NOTE:家族の記憶も…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:43.17,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:820090,823177}The day my village was attacked by the Black Blight…{NOTE:村があの黒の凶気に襲われた日から…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:45.55,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:823177,825554}…I lost everything.{NOTE:全てを失ってしまった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:47.09,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:825554,827097}I see…{NOTE:そう…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:48.26,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:827097,828265}It's all right.{NOTE:いいのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:50.60,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:828265,830601}You don't need to force yourself to remember.{NOTE:無理して思い出さなくても。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.10,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:831393,833103}But you know what, Fifi.{NOTE:でもね、ティティ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:57.39,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:833103,837399}I felt something when I came here, to Hakum Village.{NOTE:私このハクム村に来て何となく感じたの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:14:02.23,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:837399,842237}That everyone from the village I lived in was gentle and kind.{NOTE:私の住んでいた村もみんな優しくてあったかかったんだろうなって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:07.15,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:844448,847159}Oh dear! We don't have much time until sunrise.{NOTE:大変！日の出まで時間がないわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:09.16,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:847159,849161}Let's hurry and wake everyone up.{NOTE:急いでみんなを起こしましょう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:10.07,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:849161,850079}Okay.{NOTE:ええ！}
