Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:31.76,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:870599,871767}So sleepy…{NOTE:眠い…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.68,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:872643,874686}Who was it, again?{NOTE:誰だっけな～…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:37.35,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:874686,877356}The one who was looking forward the most\Nto getting up so early?{NOTE:一番早く起きるって張り切ってたのは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:41.61,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:878649,881610}I didn't think Lute was so bad at getting up.{NOTE:まさかリュートがあんなに寝起きが悪いなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:42.90,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:881610,882903}{NOTE:えっ…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.61,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:882903,884613}I'm all fine now!{NOTE:もう大丈夫だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:46.90,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:884613,886907}I feel totally awake!{NOTE:ばっちり目が覚めてるぜ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:48.86,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:886907,888867}Navirou's eyes are wide open, too!{NOTE:ナビルーもおめめぱっちりだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:50.36,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:888867,890369}Lute!{NOTE:リュート！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:50.86,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:890369,890869}{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.33,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:891954,893330}Looks like we made it in time.{NOTE:間に合ったみたいね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:22.56,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:917479,922568}May the new year be a good year!{NOTE:新しい年がいい年になりますように！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:25.77,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:922568,925779}May it be a good year!{NOTE:いい年になりますように！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:36.12,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:933662,936123}Ah, so hungry…{NOTE:あー腹減った～…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:39.25,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:936123,939251}I hope I'm not going to start\Nthe new year on empty stomach…{NOTE:まさにことし初の初腹ぺこ～…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:42.46,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:939251,942463}Then let's start the new year by making breakfast.{NOTE:じゃことし初の初朝食にしよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:43.54,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:942463,943547}I'll prepare it.{NOTE:俺が作るよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.92,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:943547,945924}Oh? But where are the Numbers?{NOTE:あれ？ナビルーたちは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:49.30,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:945924,949303}They probably wanted to start the new year by taking a walk.{NOTE:ことし初の初散歩してくるってさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:51.80,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:949303,951805}I'll be going out for a bit, too.{NOTE:私もちょっと出掛けてくるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:54.60,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:951805,954600}Lilia wanted to show me around Hakum Village.{NOTE:リリアがハクム村を案内してくれるって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:57.01,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:954600,957019}Ah, cool! Then I'll go t—{NOTE:ああ、なら俺も一緒に—}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:59.48,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:957019,959480}Ah-ha, sure! Have great time!{NOTE:ああ！ぜひ行ってくるといいよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:00.85,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:959480,960856}H-Hey.{NOTE:お…おい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:03.31,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:960856,963317}Cheval, what are you doing…?{NOTE:シュヴァル何すんだよ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:07.98,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:963317,967988}We can prepare everything while Lilia keeps Avinia busy.{NOTE:アユリアが出掛けてくれる方が俺たちだけでこっそり準備できるだろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:08.90,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:967988,968906}Oh!{NOTE:あっ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:10.78,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:969990,970782}Yeah, yeah!{NOTE:うん、うん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:13.57,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:970782,973577}Have a blast, girls!{NOTE:どうぞ、どうぞ！ゆっくり行ってくるといいよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:14.45,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:973577,974453}Okay.{NOTE:うん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:15.49,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:974453,975496}Avinia!{NOTE:アユリア！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:15.91,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:975496,975913}{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.91,Default,Loloa,0,0,0,,{TIME:977539,979917}We came to pick you up.{NOTE:迎えに来たんですの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:42.35,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:999269,1002356}Let's see… Cheval?{NOTE:え～っと、シュヴァル…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:45.98,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002356,1005984}Is it okay to mix this powder with the egg souffle?{NOTE:卵のスフレってこの粉混ぜるのでいいんだっけ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.36,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005984,1007361}Um, no.{NOTE:あ～、違うよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:48.90,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007361,1008904}Take the other one.{NOTE:もう一つの方。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.19,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008904,1010197}Oh, this one?{NOTE:こっちか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:51.24,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010197,1011240}Thank you!{NOTE:サンキュー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.19,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011240,1012199}Hey, Lute.{NOTE:ねえ、リュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.11,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012199,1013116}Yeah?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:57.32,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013116,1017329}How long should I cook the meat?{NOTE:こんがり肉ってどれくらいまでこんがりさせたらいいのかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:59.28,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017329,1019289}You cooked it too much!{NOTE:これ焦がし過ぎだって！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:00.45,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019289,1020457}Are you sure?{NOTE:そうなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:03.75,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020457,1023752}Mom always said to put meat in a good fire.{NOTE:母さんが肉には火をよく通せって言ってたから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:07.04,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023752,1027047}Well, yeah, but you overdid it.{NOTE:通し過ぎだって！ハハハッ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:18.76,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035764,1038767}Cheval, you're completely white!{NOTE:シュヴァル真っ白だぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:20.14,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038767,1040143}You should see yourself, Lute!{NOTE:リュートだって！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.39,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042521,1044398}We're home!{NOTE:ただいま～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.06,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044398,1046066}We've returned from our first walk…{NOTE:初散歩から戻った…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:28.31,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046066,1048318}Uh, what happened here?{NOTE:ってどうしたのだ!?それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:32.15,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048318,1052155}We thought it would be nice\Nto have a surprise party for Avinia.{NOTE:ｱﾕﾘｱに内緒でｻﾌﾟﾗｲｽﾞﾊﾟｰﾃｨｰをしようと思って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:35.53,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052155,1055534}So Cheval and I were trying to make a feast…{NOTE:シュヴァルと俺でごちそうを作ろうとしてて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:39.53,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055534,1059538}But can we make it like this?{NOTE:でも俺たちこんな調子でみんなのごちそう作れるかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:40.49,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059538,1060497}It'll be fine!{NOTE:大丈夫！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:41.99,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060497,1061999}As long as we put our hearts into it!{NOTE:料理はハートだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:43.00,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061999,1063000}I see!{NOTE:そっか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:44.58,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063000,1064585}You're right! It's all about heart!{NOTE:そうだよね！ハートだ！}
